<p>HUMAN RIGHTS COUNCIL 
Fourth special session  
12 December 2006 
</p>
<p><b>Albania, Australia</b>*<b>*, Austria</b>**<b>, Belgium</b>**<b>, Bosnia and Herzegovina</b>**<b>, Bulgaria</b>**<b>, 
Canada, Croatia</b>**<b>, Cyprus</b>**<b>, Czech Republic, Denmark</b>**<b>, Estonia</b>**<b>, Finland, 
